# Merge financial statements by Year
financials = income.merge(balance, on="Year", how="inner") \
                   .merge(cashflow, on="Year", how="inner")

# Sort by Year
financials = financials.sort_values("Year").reset_index(drop=True)

financials
## Data Preparation Summary

The financial statements were consolidated by year to create
a unified dataset for subsequent financial ratio analysis
and audit risk assessment.
